name: Praying for Love
description:
Location: Moni Pantheon
People come here to pray to Moni for the love of their life. Sunlight enters abundantly here. It is not too late for those who patiently perform this prayer, which lasts until the candles go out, to find true love. Popes can sometimes behave in a way that is offensive to people who pray. And if you are distracted by passing popes, you will fail. To love, you have to be persistent.
